data.description: This stunning 2,741 square foot home is nestled in the serene Cloud Country community of New Braunfels, Texas. The property boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 baths, providing ample space for a growing family or for hosting guests. The home features a dedicated office space, perfect for those who work from home, and a game room for entertainment and relaxation. The kitchen is a chef's dream with its granite countertops, white cabinets with hardware, and ceramic tile that extends throughout the wet areas and living area, ensuring easy maintenance and a sleek, modern look. This gorgeous home also includes an oversized covered patio perfect for gatherings for those hot Texas summers. The owner's suite is a true retreat with a beautiful Roman shower, offering a spa-like experience right at home. The home offers great storage which includes an oversized garage. Cloud Country offers a beautiful community pool where you can cool off and spend some time relaxing with family friends. This home perfectly combines luxury and comfort, making it a must-see property in New Braunfels, TX.
